name: Nineteen
description:
White cotton women's tee printed with black Enoyaa signature silhouette.

100% cotton.  Machine wash.
Artist's signature on left sleeve.

"Nineteen" is a silhouette I created that embodies the Enoyaa aesthetic.

***

An Enoyaa tee is both contemporary and timeless.  Enoyaa is for a girl who is always on the lookout for something new and bold to add to her wardrobe.  She is a lover of fashion and is not afraid to take risks through her use of clothing.
